Commenting:
  General:
    add standard Javadoc documentaion to classes and methods.
  Tags:
    todo - general todo tag.
    imp - needs to be implemented.
    BLOCKING - unimplemented code is blocking work elsewhere.
    
Naming:
  general:
    The naming of classes, methods, fields, etc. will follow standard Java conventions.
  Interfaces:
    Interface names will be prefaced with an 'I'. e.g. I_Name.
  Abstract classes:
    Abstract class names will be prefaced with an 'A'. e.g. A_Name.
